data.title: Plano West
data.text:
Digital PSAT/NMSQT 2024 - Plano West

*INTERESTED JUNIORS MUST REGISTER/PAY BY FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 6!

WHEN: Wednesday, October 2, 2024

WHERE: Plano West

WHO: 11th graders can sign up for the test

HOW TO REGISTER FOR THE TEST:

1- Login to Rycor Student Quick Pay

*Create a Rycor account if you are using Rycor for the first time

2- Select the “PSAT for Juniors” tile

3- Fill out the registration form

4- Go to your cart and pay the $18 exam fee online

*$11 exam fee for students participating in the free/reduced lunch program

*For additional Rycor Student Quick Pay questions, please go to the PISD website.

WHAT TO BRING TO THE EXAM: Your school-issued Chromebook, pen/pencil, and ID

*Calculators are optional. A calculator is built into the digital test.
